Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.68,0:00:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在风的节奏中推理渐渐清晰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.55,0:00:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在场证明和诡计都可以揭穿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.67,0:00:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗组织和宝石强匪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.61,0:00:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案件在抽丝剥茧中接近真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.97,0:00:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看清真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.65,0:00:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表看似小孩 智慧却过于常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.55,0:00:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字就叫做 名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.22,0:01:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从被杀害的板仓先生的日记中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.92,0:01:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解到有关黑暗组织的线索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.69,0:01:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我和博士来到了板仓的别墅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.84,0:01:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在那里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.93,0:02:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.56,0:02:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伏特加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.69,0:02:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.46,0:02:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被发现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.95,0:02:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在这别墅里没收邮件的事被发现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.41,0:02:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.70,0:02:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！快说话啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.77,0:02:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你就在别墅里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.02,0:02:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新…新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.66,0:02:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点回答我 板仓先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.52,0:02:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.01,0:02:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与黑暗组织的接触（追迹篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.24,0:02:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！快说话啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.59,0:02:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你就在别墅里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.00,0:02:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点回答我 板仓先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.34,0:02:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽…虽然有点危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.15,0:03:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也只能冒着暴风雪从后门溜出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.19,0:03:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…真是抱歉 在黑暗中一时找不到电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.88,0:03:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.49,0:03:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里好像因为暴风雪来袭而停电了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.53,0:03:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以刚刚的邮件没有接收
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.59,0:03:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫你跑到深山的别墅去接收邮件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.35,0:03:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！等一下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.02,0:03:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果停电为什么答录机还能启动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.08,0:03:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 因为一下雪这里经常会停电
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.45,0:03:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我使用了内部装电池的电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.27,0:03:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.21,0:03:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你知道的还真清楚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.60,0:03:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这里的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.94,0:03:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的一举一动都在我们的掌握之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.44,0:03:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,350)\fad(300,300)}（把灯打开）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.11,0:03:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不会一直在监视这栋别墅吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.77,0:03:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.60,0:03:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有监视
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.61,0:04:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和约好的一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.75,0:04:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不会骚扰你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.51,0:04:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 你完成了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.64,0:04:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个软件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.40,0:04:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.00,0:04:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？有人在你旁边吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.83,0:04:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说话啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.45,0:04:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚是什么声音？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.27,0:04:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.28,0:04:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是风的声音 刚刚风打到窗户的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.12,0:04:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因为你那边的雪下得很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.64,0:04:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我现在无法使用电脑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.02,0:04:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你就直接告诉我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.06,0:04:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交软件的时间和地点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.56,0:04:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼！没办法 我可只说一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.11,0:04:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你仔细听好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.80,0:04:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道有个还在施工中的贤桥车站吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.46,0:04:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是以后道路和地铁的连结点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.50,0:04:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天凌晨12点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.59,0:04:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那个车站最下层的0032寄物柜前碰面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.04,0:05:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘了带那个软件来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.02,0:05:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.88,0:05:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明天不方便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.92,0:05:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.52,0:05:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天下午办了住院手续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.53,0:05:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也知道我的心脏不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.51,0:05:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会还没完成那个软件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.52,0:05:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想借机拖延时间吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.25,0:05:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能？我已经完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.62,0:05:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你哪天方便？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.73,0:05:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大概要住3到4天 可能要5天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.54,0:05:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！我可等不了那么久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.99,0:05:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去延迟你的住院时间吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.76,0:05:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经预约了一位著名的心脏外科医生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.38,0:05:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法改时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.44,0:05:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你要我在住院前交给你的话就只有今晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.45,0:05:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天的话工人会到车站工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.90,0:05:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这样反而对你们不利吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.62,0:05:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就4点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.95,0:05:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四个小时之后也就是凌晨4点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.54,0:06:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把软件带到我刚刚讲的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.84,0:06:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四、四个小时？要我从群马赶到东京？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.39,0:06:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.67,0:06:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然已经完成了 应该可以拿来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.97,0:06:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.77,0:06:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会在四个小时后抵达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.47,0:06:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你们不准在那里提前埋伏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.86,0:06:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我看到了你们的同伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.04,0:06:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此次交易立刻终止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.32,0:06:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你们要硬抢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.96,0:06:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也永远不会知道这个软件怎么用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.45,0:06:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼！和了解的一样 你这个人还真是谨慎啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.67,0:06:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么四个小时以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.46,0:06:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在贤桥车站地下的0032寄物柜前碰面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.55,0:06:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万别迟到哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.25,0:06:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.24,0:06:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 上钩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.50,0:06:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你到底想干什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.78,0:06:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你真的要听他们的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.85,0:06:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把软件拿去给他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.53,0:07:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会听他们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.88,0:07:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是引诱他把交货时间提前到凌晨4点而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.99,0:07:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假装着急的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.54,0:07:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.44,0:07:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天亮之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.78,0:07:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新闻不就开始报导板仓先生被杀的消息了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.74,0:07:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事要是被那些家伙们知道的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.57,0:07:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个交易和那些家伙的线索可能又会断了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.60,0:07:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好目前还没有媒体报导板仓的新闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.35,0:07:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你一开始就这么打算吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.56,0:07:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.68,0:07:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来就打算收到他们的邮件之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.67,0:07:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上回信要求提早交易的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.44,0:07:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.44,0:07:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点把我们到过这里的所有痕迹擦掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.75,0:07:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后博士你去开车我们赶紧离开这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.85,0:07:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.86,0:07:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那些家伙不是在附近监视这里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.25,0:07:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我们光明正大地开着车离开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.82,0:07:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙说不定会看见我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.83,0:07:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.54,0:08:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果伏特加和他的同伙在监视这栋房子的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.93,0:08:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为停电而无法使用电脑的这句谎话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.55,0:08:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定马上就会知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.74,0:08:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.42,0:08:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才叫我把灯打开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.41,0:08:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.65,0:08:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来至少可以肯定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.15,0:08:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近没有他们的同伙在监视
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.40,0:08:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们之所以会知道这个地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.15,0:08:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是安装了收件者没有打开邮件的情况下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.12,0:08:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会自动追踪收件人所在地的系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.20,0:08:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少已经掌握到那些家伙的线索了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.40,0:08:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来只要用博士车上的手提电脑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.92,0:08:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,检查这个软件里的内容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.86,0:08:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是能用来记录犯下的重大案件的资料的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.83,0:08:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就马上通知警察埋伏在交易地点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.55,0:08:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到他们来拿软件时就能一网打尽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.17,0:08:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.46,0:09:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 不行！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.36,0:09:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个软件也被设定了密码
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.82,0:09:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟那封邮件一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.23,0:09:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能板仓和那些家伙事先设定了密码
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.70,0:09:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就先复制起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.38,0:09:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.85,0:09:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为复制档案也需要密码
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.01,0:09:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来就没有证据给警方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.92,0:09:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙不是经常带着枪吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.26,0:09:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就用非法携带枪械的名义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.98,0:09:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样警方至少会出动两三名警察吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.09,0:09:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我们不知道对方会来多少人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.32,0:09:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来太危险了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.10,0:09:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本打算找出他们的犯罪证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.10,0:09:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让警方知道是一个多么庞大的组织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.43,0:09:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去破坏他们的计划并逮捕他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.42,0:09:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是现在已经不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.15,0:09:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是急死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.99,0:09:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知道那些家伙会在那里出现却无计可施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.46,0:09:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.40,0:09:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一个方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.40,0:10:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.99,0:10:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…你该不会想直接跟他们见面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.08,0:10:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 博士…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.80,0:10:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这该不会是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.52,0:10:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 大概吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.89,0:10:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然应该事先准备备用胎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.12,0:10:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好打电话给离这里最近的加油站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.93,0:10:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请他们马上送轮胎过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.14,0:10:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.73,0:10:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时候在这个地方不可能马上过来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.55,0:10:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看我们就坐在车里慢慢等好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.45,0:10:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就赶不上交易时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.18,0:10:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一定是神叫新一你不要去做那么危险的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.49,0:10:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.42,0:10:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车…车子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.23,0:10:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.73,0:10:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.39,0:10:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.89,0:11:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…我的车子爆胎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.74,0:11:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想回到东京去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.24,0:11:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以载我们一程吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.11,0:11:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东京？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.73,0:11:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.10,0:11:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 反正顺路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.21,0:11:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 这附近的路你熟悉吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.71,0:11:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 还可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.69,0:11:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么大叔就坐在副驾驶上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.41,0:11:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小弟弟就坐后面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.34,0:11:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.20,0:11:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊 大姐姐 吵到你睡觉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.26,0:11:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 我只是躺一会儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.96,0:11:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.59,0:11:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是外国车吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.34,0:11:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大哥哥你的车吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.61,0:11:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 已经开得有点腻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.27,0:11:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近正想换一部新车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.87,0:12:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你一定很有钱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.78,0:12:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这车很贵的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.27,0:12:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还可以啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.53,0:12:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去不怎么样他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.97,0:12:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是一个大公司的继承人哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.00,0:12:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.23,0:12:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.89,0:12:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.82,0:12:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,积雪的道路真是可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.58,0:12:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要急 安全驾驶最重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.45,0:12:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.35,0:12:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问你们刚刚有没有听到奇怪的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.22,0:12:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有吗？我什么也没听到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.59,0:12:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是堆在后车箱的行李吧 不要介意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.35,0:12:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！不要吸烟！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.71,0:12:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.49,0:12:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌烟味！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.53,0:12:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉 我一时忘记了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.36,0:12:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往东京的方向要向左转
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.74,0:13:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.31,0:13:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪已经停了 我想3点前应该可以到了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.29,0:13:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你们为什么来群马县？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.54,0:13:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带孙子来滑雪吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.75,0:13:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不算是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.19,0:13:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.91,0:13:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你专心开好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.04,0:13:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.38,0:13:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不该走积雪的道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.89,0:13:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.22,0:13:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在太奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.48,0:13:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.79,0:13:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说这两个人是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.59,0:14:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小心一点好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.39,0:14:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才开始已经有不少车子向我们按喇叭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.32,0:14:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不是说过了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.67,0:14:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不擅长在雪路上开车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.42,0:14:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 大哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.14,0:14:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这辆车还没进行车检
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.56,0:14:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要更小心开车啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.83,0:14:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这辆车差不多该车检了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.74,0:14:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.28,0:14:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.07,0:14:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不记得了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.02,0:14:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车窗前的挡风玻璃上不是写着“2”的标志吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.67,0:14:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个标志叫做车检标志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.83,0:14:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用数字和颜色提示人们什么时候该去车检
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.49,0:14:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的标志颜色是今年的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.41,0:14:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你应该要在今年2月份之前去做车检才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.29,0:14:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我想起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.56,0:15:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个月我刚收到去做车检的通知单
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.91,0:15:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是小弟弟 那个标志你什么时候看见的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.77,0:15:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它应该都被雪盖住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.48,0:15:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.43,0:15:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要对面有车开来就可以看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.05,0:15:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透过车灯的光线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.99,0:15:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能看到表面的数字了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.15,0:15:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.92,0:15:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是从背面看到的“2”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.02,0:15:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实应该是“5”才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.52,0:15:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过好奇怪哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.05,0:15:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥你怎么会收到2月之前做车检的通知呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.55,0:15:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.11,0:15:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不…那是因为…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.74,0:15:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是跟你们说过了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.99,0:15:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个有钱的少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.36,0:15:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那些事都是交给别人去做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.10,0:15:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他刚才是随便说说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.91,0:15:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实他自己根本从没注意过车检的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.34,0:15:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有在这里右转的话要到东京可就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.56,0:16:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 都是小弟弟你太啰嗦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.90,0:16:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 这个孩子的好奇心就是太旺盛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.24,0:16:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 这也没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.54,0:16:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.00,0:16:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才开始你一直在听什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.27,0:16:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这个吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.71,0:16:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收音机的新闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.43,0:16:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新闻？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.71,0:16:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 报道了很多的新闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.75,0:16:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是景气复苏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.04,0:16:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BIG大阪队的新教练
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.34,0:16:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有逃亡中的宝石抢匪等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.09,0:16:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不简单啊 这么小的年龄就喜欢听新闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.84,0:16:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.85,0:16:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢？那个宝石抢匪落网了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.15,0:16:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新闻报道说他们可能还在群马县附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.34,0:16:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过一定可以马上被逮捕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.59,0:17:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看现在到处都有路检
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.65,0:17:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请出示驾照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.08,0:17:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问您是从哪里过来的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.00,0:17:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.72,0:17:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这不是山村警官吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.37,0:17:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是柯南吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.52,0:17:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山村警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.34,0:17:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是为了抓住宝石抢匪所设的路检对不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.80,0:17:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.30,0:17:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那三个抢匪带着面具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.97,0:17:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抢劫了一家珠宝店之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.69,0:17:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们把作案用的赃车丢弃在山里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.02,0:17:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就消失的无影无踪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.01,0:17:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那三个人里其中一个人受了伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.06,0:17:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想应该不会逃得太远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.82,0:17:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受了伤？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.35,0:18:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.66,0:18:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到消息时我正好在附近巡逻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.32,0:18:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从宝石店跑出的抢匪被我撞了个正着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.76,0:18:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我拿出枪冲着他们大喊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.75,0:18:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 不然的话我就要开枪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.58,0:18:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.52,0:18:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帅呆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.76,0:18:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他们不听警告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.45,0:18:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就开了一枪打算吓唬他们一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.01,0:18:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.65,0:18:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样 没想到刚好打中其中一名犯人的腿上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.80,0:18:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咳咳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.90,0:18:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咳…总之他们可能是开着事先准备好的其他车辆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.11,0:18:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是抢了路上来往的车子逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.21,0:18:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 你们有没有看到这种可疑的家伙吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.71,0:18:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.77,0:18:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是坐在别人车上的人对不对？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.99,0:18:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我们啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.27,0:19:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的车在山中坏掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.68,0:19:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请刚好路过的这位先生让我们搭个便车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.96,0:19:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就…就是这么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.56,0:19:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿笠先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.87,0:19:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你的车呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.95,0:19:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打电话给修车场 他们说早上才会把车开走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.74,0:19:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我把钥匙挂在车上扔到山里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.77,0:19:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样你的车不是很危险吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.77,0:19:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被那些抢匪发现说不定会开走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.65,0:19:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个很有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.36,0:19:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你不用管我们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.67,0:19:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是快去看看那辆车比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.86,0:19:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一台黄色的金龟车很好找的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.27,0:19:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真奇怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.89,0:19:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像在哪里听到过你们的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.24,0:19:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.93,0:19:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以走了吗 警官？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.64,0:19:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 盖在你大腿上的外套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.21,0:19:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以拿下来吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.36,0:19:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在怀疑我们？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.36,0:20:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看没有中枪的痕迹吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.46,0:20:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 那么路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.24,0:20:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 这里是阿笠家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.52,0:20:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,群马县警察？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.18,0:20:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然阿笠先生已经叫修车厂早上来把车子开走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.64,0:20:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我怕车子继续放在山里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.07,0:20:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能会被逃亡中的抢匪开走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.41,0:20:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此先叫吊车把车子移开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.82,0:20:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请转告他来群马县警局这边取车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.95,0:20:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.80,0:20:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.95,0:20:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.78,0:20:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么晚了干嘛要开车去群马？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.14,0:21:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定又是被工藤找去调查某件案件去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.83,0:21:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪费睡觉的时间管那么多闲事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.92,0:21:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侦探真的有那么好玩吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.92,0:21:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,备用的追踪眼镜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.86,0:21:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 交货的时间提前了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.64,0:21:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间是一小时后的零晨4点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.49,0:21:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地点不变还是在贤桥车站地下寄物柜前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.11,0:21:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟琴酒说一声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.71,0:21:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这是当然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.52,0:21:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多找点人手 带枪来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.95,0:22:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙说不定会吓得叫警方过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.85,0:22:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我们原本就打算在交易后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.20,0:22:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在贤桥车站把他干掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.28,0:23:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 时间快到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.24,0:23:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都到齐了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.42,0:23:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.40,0:23:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连一只老鼠也不准放过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.45,0:24:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.92,0:24:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 还在这附近窥视着呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.65,0:24:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.00,0:24:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与黑暗组织的接触（决死篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.99,0:24:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN'S HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.34,0:24:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄物柜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.47,0:24:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回终于要和他们见面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.34,0:24:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得意忘形可不太好哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.21,0:24:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.72,0:00:30.02,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海风中感觉到你的气息 银色的波浪消除了二人的距离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.73,0:00:43.92,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样让时间停止吧 远远看去藐小的街道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.29,0:00:53.39,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经无法再分离 与你约定在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.63,0:01:00.98,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在闪耀的季节中得来不易的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.09,0:01:08.19,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再迷惘 相信我的眼神 风的啦啦啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.31,0:01:15.78,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在溢满的不安中隐藏泪水的昨天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.98,0:01:25.80,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥远的回忆现在终于可以说出 风的啦啦啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.34,0:22:35.23,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到你的电话声 如此坚强的我也会哭泣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.35,0:22:42.57,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管彼此伤害对方 但是还是想见到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.75,0:22:48.33,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使结局终究令人厌恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.61,0:22:55.97,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对于给我的回答觉得为难吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.54,0:23:04.05,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次回想起你那无法掩藏的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.58,0:23:08.05,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…I miss you
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.21,0:23:21.93,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想明天 希望能够相信 即使路途坎坷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.23,0:23:30.58,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想明天 你的全部 希望能够见到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.77,0:23:39.18,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又到了只剩树荫间阳光摇曳的日子
